					</li>
					<li>
						Managed $250K annual marketing budget, optimizing spend across
						advertising, trade shows, and contractors.
					</li>
					<li>
						Directed certification and regulatory approval processes (FCC, CE),
						overseeing documentation and labeling compliance for global markets.
					</li>
					<li>
						Maintained vendor relationships across four time zones, reducing
