						>Apr 2019 - Jun 2021</span
					>
				</div>
				<div class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700">
					Kepro Healthcare CM & QIO (Remote)
				</div>
				<ul
					class="ml-4 list-outside list-disc space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700"
				>
					<li>
						Directed marketing and creative production for 30+ healthcare
						proposals, including deliverables for Pfizer and State of Florida.
					</li>
					<li>
						Executed global localization for Pfizer campaigns in 25 languages
						across 88 countries.
					</li>
					<li>
						Maintained centralized content library and version-control system,
						reducing rework and supporting audits.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- Job 3 -->
			<div class="mb-6">
				<div class="mb-1 flex items-baseline justify-between">
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">
						Senior Content Specialist
					</h4>
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500"
						>Jul 2008 - Aug 2018</span
					>
				</div>
				<div class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700">
					AAAS / Science Magazine
				</div>
				<ul
					class="ml-4 list-outside list-disc space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700"
				>
					<li>
						Created layout workflows that cut processing time and saved ~$50K
						annually in paper/print costs.
					</li>
					<li>
						Coordinated design and editorial teams to launch mobile-responsive
						app for 30,000+ readers.
					</li>
					<li>
						Implemented collaborative scheduling systems that eliminated
						publication delays.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Education & Tools -->
		<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
			<section>
				<h3
					class="mb-3 border-b border-gray-100 pb-1 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider text-slate-500 uppercase"
				>
					Education
				</h3>
				<div class="mb-3">
					<h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Lake Forest College</h4>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">B.A., Philosophy</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Brown College</h4>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">A.A.S., Visual Communications</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h3
					class="mb-3 border-b border-gray-100 pb-1 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider text-slate-500 uppercase"
				>
					Tools
				</h3>
				<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
					Adobe Creative Suite (InDesign, Photoshop, Illustrator) • Figma •
					WordPress • GA4 • Workfront • Jira • Trello • HubSpot • Microsoft 365
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Back to Home Bottom Link -->
	<div class="mt-12 text-center">
		<a
			href="#home"
			class="nav-link text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
			data-target="home">← Back to Home</a
		>
	</div>
</div>

<style>
	/* Resume Paper Styles */
	.resume-paper {
		box-shadow:
			0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
			0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
	}
	.dark .resume-paper {
		box-shadow:
			0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5),
			0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
	}
</style>

<script>
	const dropdownBtn = document.getElementById("download-menu-btn");
	const dropdownMenu = document.getElementById("download-menu");

	dropdownBtn?.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
		e.stopPropagation();
		dropdownMenu?.classList.toggle("hidden");
	});

	// Close dropdown when clicking outside
	document.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
		if (
			dropdownBtn &&
			dropdownMenu &&
			!dropdownBtn.contains(e.target as Node) &&
			!dropdownMenu.contains(e.target as Node)
		) {
			dropdownMenu.classList.add("hidden");
		}
	});
</script>
